This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with 3D perception problems such as object/scene recognition and augmented reality. It is also likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it mentions autonomous navigation and SLAM. The use of Gaussian Mixture Models (GMM) suggests that it could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of parallel processing on a GPU suggests that it could also belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
